Title: Construction of Perturbatively Correct Light Front Hamiltonian for  (2+1)-Dimensional Gauge Theory
Authors: M. Yu. Malyshev and E. V. Prokhvatilov and R. A. Zubov and V. A. Franke
Abstract: In this paper we consider (2+1)-dimensional SU(N)-symmetric gauge theory within light front perturbation theory, regularized by the method analogous to Pauli-Villars regularization. This enables us to construct correct renormalized light front Hamiltonian.
